Sonic Sensor only has a maximum range of about 5 meters or so; it also becomes less reliable when the object is not a large uniform wall.

TFT LCDs come in various sizes that may have different hardware requirements.

Some modules have "worn out" during operation, such as the microSD module (originally purchased for a dollar). 
Multiple copies of such modules should be purchased as back-ups.
It takes quite a while for them to ship from their source, which is usually China.
